  "sourceOfTruthCutover": {
    "canonicalNextSlice": "PrehistoricRush Dino Domain Bridge + Runtime Authority Fixture Gate",
    "problem": "src/game.js has introduced a domain runtime and dino domain kits, but src/runtime-terrain-v6.mjs still owns live runner math, raptor creation, raptor animation, input semantics, contact outcomes, spawn budgets, win threshold, scene transitions, and host diagnostics inline. The existing dino-pose-domain-kit listens for runner.moved, but the live runner never emits runner.moved yet.",
